<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="grateful-adj">grateful <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ɡreɪtfl/    美 /'ɡreɪtfl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>感激的；感谢的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We are very <strong>grateful to</strong> you for what you did for us<strong>for_1</strong>
我们对你为我们所做的一切深表感谢。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>I would be grateful if you could</strong> give me a kind consideration.
如果你能考虑我的话，我将不胜感激。</p><footer>2015 陕西书面表达改</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>I'm so grateful<strong><em>_</em></strong>_ all those volunteers because they helped my terrible day end happily.  （2015 安徽改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. to  </p></div>